{"tid":933498,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★上海法院以間諜罪判一日本人六年監禁","createTime":"2018-12-08T14:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T17:12:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d39fca28faae5d99183c8b7d6a779e2ff9fd7f42","tid":933498,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名日本女子在中國被控間諜罪，判處六年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報道，涉案57歲女子在中國出生，取得日本國籍後在東京一間日語學校工作，不時會在中國招募留學生。她在2015年於上海被捕，翌年被起訴間諜罪。<br />\n<br />\n上海第一中級人民法院周五判處她六年有期徒刑，沒收財產五萬元人民幣，並於服刑後將她驅逐出境，當局至今未有公布她涉及甚麼間諜行為。<br />\n<br />\n中方近年對在境內活動的海外組織和個人加強監視，自2015年起先後以間諜罪起訴八名日本人，其中三人已被判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=330045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D330045&d=3EKZTjU1yvnhV9EH%2F%2F6VWkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=ee35e854\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D330045&h=bfb6cc94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=330045</a>"},{"pid":"3be3d722bbeccf46291c88bb55732e5c81232970","tid":933498,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"俾安倍撚完狗，依家報復"},{"pid":"ae18af52c14fb8cabf580da7f0a6718273aec1d4","tid":933498,"uid":20473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"57歲女子在中國出生<br />\n57歲女子在中國出生"},{"pid":"1f99218be964ae1bbc4efe76780dcc2d72558323","tid":933498,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"沒收財產五萬元人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea644b0133872d403bc47085bbfbb2b045f2f21a","tid":933498,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0